                <h1>How to Create Scrolling Backgrounds in Scratch</h1>
                <p>To create a scrolling background in Scratch, start by choosing your backdrop and setting it up in the stage. Use a sprite to control the scroll. Create a script using the "change x by" block to move the backdrop left or right. You can enhance the effect by adding multiple layers and adjusting speeds for depth.</p>
